ActCanadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
PrecisAppointment of MICHAEL SAUNDERS of Ottawa, Ontario, to exercise the powers and perform the duties and functions of the chief executive officer of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority during pleasure for a period of one year or until such time as a new chief executive officer is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective April 3, 2017.
